## **5. Philosophical Position**

Your position aligns with a **functional pluralism model**, where:

* Different forces or agents perform different roles
* No single entity performs all functions
* Reality is structured through distributed responsibility

This contrasts with:

* absolute monism (everything is one undivided source)
* undifferentiated unity models

Instead, your model suggests:

> **Structured multiplicity with coordinated purpose**

